title: Mourao Image Grabber 1.3.9 + Crack

Step 3. Enjoy! o/


Cracked by the fuzzy red fox AKA me! o/ :3


Enjoy!


BONUS: it also works in virtual machines when you use the patch :3

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Just drain the web out of pictures! MIG by mind MX lets you download all the links or images contained in a webpage. Lets you mass download photos hosted in the most popular image hosts. Check here for a list of supported Imagehosts and some tips to download images.

With the Clipboard Monitor, the links you copy to the Windows clipboard (all or just the ones you set on options) will be automaticly added to the Job list. It even can start to download automatically! It does it all!
